<h3>How do I structure my data for Mettle to use?</h3>

<p>Normal CSV files work fine - although there are some constraints
	<ul>
    <li> Fields in the files can be separated using any delimiter</li>
	  <li> Mixed delimiters (e.g. some fields comma separated and others tab separated) are not supported</li>
    <li> Each file must have its column names in the first row </li>
	  <li> Both files must have the same column names</li>
	</ul>

<p>Please <%= link_to "let us know", feedback_path %> if you have problems loading your data.</p>

